Privacy Policy
We collect and retain the least information necessary to send you a weather forecast and debug any occasional problems that might arise.
Information Collection and Use:
Our Apps does not collect any personal information about you, your app usage, and/or your website usage. Other third parties, including but not limited to Apple, may be collecting your data. This data may include your device's Internet Protocol ("IP") address, browser type, browser version, the type of app, the time and date of your use, the time spent on those pages, and other statistics.
Third parties, including but not limited to Apple, may also collect your information for advertising purposes. To learn more about how Apple (iAd) uses your data and how you can opt-out of their Limited Ad Tracking, please visit:
https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT202074
.
Cookies:
Our Apps does not collect any personal information about you, your app usage, and/or your website usage and therefore does not use cookies. Third parties, including but not limited to Apple, may be placing and reading cookies on users' browsers, or using web beacons to collect information as a result of ads serving on our apps and websites.
Changes to This Privacy Policy:
This policy is subject to change without notice. Please check this page for the latest privacy policy. If you disagree with this policy, please discontinue use of the application.